REAndroid/APKEditor.Changelog:
## What's Changed
* Support dex versions upto 40 #100 
* Fix: Correct order of resource config flags: https://github.com/REAndroid/ARSCLib/commit/3c31e3e37f19227b7957621a6c82dc7385da6c64
